summary:
I am high skilled professional JavaScript developer with great experience in Web technologies.
* 12+ years web development experience
* 8+ years frontend development experience

I prefer to write testable, maintainable and clean code. I love being a part of a great team with smart, interesting and creative people. I keep my mind open for new technologies and prefer to be familiar with new trends.

Skills:
JavaScript, TypeScript, React, Redux, AngularJS, Webpack, Jest, ESLint, Node.js, HTML, CSS, PostCSS, SCSS, LESS, Bootstrap, PHP, Symfony, MySQL, Postgres, Redis, Docker, Git

My github: https://github.com/igorzoriy
